{"tid":2507401,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疫苗氣泡︱逼員工顧客打針巡查人員卻毋須接種 ! ! !","createTime":"2021-04-28T03:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T04:02:07.000Z","uid":73071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7917554d504d44cd23761a8050f5346387a45056","tid":2507401,"uid":73071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"&quot;政府昨公佈明日起推出疫苗氣泡，將食肆分為4類別，想放寬防疫措施的食肆則必須要員工及顧客接種疫苗。食環署署長楊碧筠今早在電台節目中指，餐廳內可同時並行B、C及D類模式，但食肆要向署方申報平面圖，方便執法人員巡查時區分區域。問到巡查的執法人員需否同樣要接種疫苗，楊未有正面回應，僅稱會根據公務員事務局指引行事。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/K7GNK2HMOFHZLBVV44CBRWSE5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FK7GNK2HMOFHZLBVV44CBRWSE5A%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=9c582cf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FK7GNK2HMOFHZLBVV44CBRWSE5A%2F&h=1c403196\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/K7GNK2HMOFHZLBVV44CBRWSE5A/</a>"},{"pid":"ba6b7ba9e711a348c53a6b64515bc890433dc40e","tid":2507401,"uid":73071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"港共淨係會逼其他人打針<br />\n公務員有幾多人打咗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62254e71db7cf4cf37a8e8b0ea7e917a2b3e6054","tid":2507401,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"食環狗自己都唔撚打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2581cfbc93abef9ea27775cc71edf446afecf021","tid":2507401,"uid":157588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"食環狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974c8d745daa0c1183e5bb0619c6952fb3f8ba1f","tid":2507401,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":